title: Did The Warriors Change The Series?
description:
Pablo Torre, Domonique Foxworth and Spencer Hall debate if the Warriors’ win last night changed the way you expect the rest of the series to unfold and if Rafael Nadal separated himself from Djokovic and Federer yesterday.
